{"id": 2820, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得自己的工作/专业有哪些「无法被机器人取代」的地方？", "description": "至少，机器人暂时还是学不会像我一样摸鱼啊。（题图来自：iStock ️©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 2370, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190304165606JjIxr2zbKgXLE8h7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-14T03:00:22Z", "options": [{"id": 333314, "content": "断货之后，机器人不能背锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 82890}, {"id": 333315, "content": "我都不知道自己干了什么，也就不可能知道是否会被机器人替代！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609281}, {"id": 333827, "content": "机器人可以模仿人的思考过程，但无法具备人的思维；机器人可以记录和推测人的行为，但无法感知人内心深处的追求和渴望，也无法帮他们克服追求目标过程中的懒惰、懦弱或激进", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612837}, {"id": 333316, "content": "委婉型社交行为", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738443}, {"id": 333317, "content": "我是潜水教练，机器人来做难度很大", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573164}, {"id": 333318, "content": "机器人不会享受生活。不能帮人体验。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254465}, {"id": 333574, "content": "机器人没有情感，不会揣摩人的心理 😂，比如言外之意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475593}, {"id": 337926, "content": "没有感情没有心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 333319, "content": "没有！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753653}, {"id": 333577, "content": "他会五彩斑斓黑吗\n好像真的会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 333322, "content": "一本正经的胡说八道啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609328}, {"id": 333323, "content": "机器人不会造词…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 432048}, {"id": 333324, "content": "？程序员？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898852}, {"id": 333325, "content": "机器人  不能自己写代码\n（你已经是个成熟的编译器了  不能自己写代码或者改bug吗？？？）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032942}, {"id": 333326, "content": "拍领导马屁哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336961}, {"id": 333327, "content": "我是银行信贷人员，也许人工智能可以取代我们的办贷流程，也许唯一不能被取代的就是人与人之间的那点温暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609348}, {"id": 333328, "content": "机器人无法Debug", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609357}, {"id": 333585, "content": "机器人可能不会感性地作出很多妥协，为了人际关系为了各部门人员之间最简单的互助和谐以至于后期项目的成功，可我能", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437075}, {"id": 333330, "content": "机器人不能让繁殖器官碰撞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609343}, {"id": 333842, "content": "机器人不会推理论！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612947}, {"id": 333332, "content": "我是做动画设计的 比较靠主观设计。我想机器不能代替", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609377}, {"id": 333333, "content": "应用心理学(我的专业哈哈哈哈)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1591457}, {"id": 333334, "content": "它写不出我真实感受和体验过的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609394}, {"id": 333337, "content": "睡觉……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654678}, {"id": 338457, "content": "共情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633926}, {"id": 333339, "content": "眼力劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084711}, {"id": 333340, "content": "我可爱啊(⁎⁍̴̛ᴗ⁍̴̛⁎)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609426}, {"id": 333342, "content": "他们无法创新 他们有学习能力 有强大当的计算能力 但他们决定不能创造新的东西\n特别是艺术类的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609425}, {"id": 333598, "content": "语言的沟通不是简单的回答", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547709}, {"id": 334110, "content": "不能舔上级，对上级的“指教”无法适当回应（我也做不好）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305661}, {"id": 333349, "content": "烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1550591}, {"id": 333350, "content": "机器人韧带不好", "image": "img/option/option/20190314235943I8eODg7FiWQJzMcd.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609430}, {"id": 334887, "content": "发现大部分回答都是搞怪的，机器做不到吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439574}, {"id": 333357, "content": "你什么意思 意思意思 哈哈 那我就不好意思了 请问这是什么意思？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155866}, {"id": 333358, "content": "机器人不会犯错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297626}, {"id": 335406, "content": "抛去理性，带入人性的思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603045}, {"id": 333361, "content": "中国是人情社会……\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609476}, {"id": 333617, "content": "仁者见仁 智者见智  我认为在我的主观判断里 只要你自己认为无法替代就是无法替代的 \n画画亦是如此 无论电脑的软件再强大 也无法表达出我在画面中每一根线条所表达的情感  我不排斥带给我的便利 但“取代”这个词我不是很喜欢 存在即有存在的道理 别涉及到“七情六欲”\n", "image": "img/option/option/20190318010750Rs0vVzejD7ryuiCN.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611793}, {"id": 333619, "content": "灵魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547567}, {"id": 333364, "content": "学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499206}, {"id": 333365, "content": "同类之间的任何有感情的交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609517}, {"id": 333621, "content": "AI是生物吗？狗狗这种生物都会摸鱼画饼，高端智能没有理由不会。AI代替我们，是进化的后果，你们现在心目中的AI都太小了，看起来就像是一台计算机。而我认为，计算机只是其中的一个原子。他要永生，就需要逃离地球。就像我们如果逃离地球需要带上长颈鹿和大象一样，他们需要带上人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611847}, {"id": 333366, "content": "我是做设计的 这类创造性工作应该无法被取代 毕竟机器人恐怕“想”出新东西会有点困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513995}, {"id": 333623, "content": "不如我沙雕……\n然而我还连工作都没有呢🌚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490130}, {"id": 333368, "content": "不懂风水，不懂中医", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609529}, {"id": 333370, "content": "发明机器人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553647}, {"id": 333371, "content": "不会换位思考，教学这方面没办法达到人教学的效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609527}, {"id": 333372, "content": "机器人不会对文物抱有感情，不能从中感受到历史的伟大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1607391}, {"id": 336701, "content": "机器人不能自己编写程序", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623699}, {"id": 333375, "content": "机器人学不会上班摸鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1609564}]}